❗️The State Power Committee held a round table in the Volyn region on the topic: "Participation of local self-government bodies in international territorial cooperation within the framework of the process of accession to the European Union", dedicated to studying the experience of territorial communities of Ukraine and, in particular, communities of Volyn and Rivne region. The subject of discussion were the following questions: - legislative regulation of the sphere of international cooperation and prospects for its improvement through the draft Law of Ukraine "On International Territorial Cooperation of Ukraine" (No. 9450); - access to European funds and investments within the framework of the implementation of the EU Cohesion Policy for the program period 2022-2027;
-participation of local government in projects and programs of international cooperation, development of an algorithm for finding a potential partner, etc.

Particular attention was paid to familiarization with the experience of Lithuania in the field of international cooperation and the future cooperation of the territorial communities of Volyn and Rivne region with the communities of Lithuania. 📲Details
